The paper deals with image reconstruction using deep learned priors, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV). The use of Fourier space and non-linear annihilation relations suggests that the paper may also fall under information theory (cs.IT). The use of deep learning also suggests that the paper may fall under machine learning (cs.LG). The paper deals with image reconstruction, which is a common topic in multimedia (cs.MM). Finally, the paper may also fall under signal processing (cs.SI) due to its use of Fourier space.
